title: Week 3 Watch List and Last-Second Fantasy Advice | GM Street (Ep. 306)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss the Browns' victory over the Jets (02:00), before highlighting some of their favorite games coming up this weekend (09:45). Then Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly of 'The Dantasy Football Podcast' give out some last-second fantasy advice (36:00).
